search_results.title: Person - Clemmy the Brave's Website
search_results.snippet: Clemmy, the most famous bulldog in the world, introduces us to her person. The one who feeds her houses her and helps her type.

search_results.title: Clemmy the Brave's Website: Home
search_results.snippet: Meet Clemmy the Brave, the most famous bulldog in the world! The only one with four books, a website, a blog, and a YouTube channel!

search_results.title: Clemmy The Brave: Clemmy Learns to Talk
search_results.snippet: In this delightful full-color Christian children's book, Clemmy the bulldog learns to talk and to listen—and her people learn the same.
